                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Brown</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.—Extracts.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-07-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 13, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Brown reports he has just had a conference with President Estrada, who
                    accepts in principle the proposal of peace, but doubts good faith of Salvador,
                    and insists the agreement to disarm and negotiate must be pledged satisfactorily
                    to the United States Government. Instructions are requested.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
